.DS_Store
# `weights/*` (not `weights/`) so the exceptions below can match files inside.
# Git won't recurse into a fully-ignored directory.
weights/*
# DO commit the small weights for the alternate ONNX backends. Pyannote's
# model.onnx (5.7 MB) is still downloaded by setup.sh; fsmn-vad + firered-vad
# total ~4 MB and are bundled so `bin/vad -backend fsmn|firered` works out of
# the box. Regen via speax/benchmarks/vad/export_*_to_onnx.py if needed.
!weights/fsmn-vad/
!weights/firered-vad/
/vad
third_party/
*.f32
# DO commit fbank parity-test fixtures (small, needed for `go test ./fbank` to work)
!fbank/testdata/*.f32
cmd/pkg-example/pkg-example
cmd/pkg-example/segmented-output/
cmd/pkg-example/unsegmented-output/
cmd/pkg-example/input/
cmd/basic-vad-web/basic-vad-web
